Subject: [PATCH 04/19] =?UTF-8?q?wasm:=20fs=20shim=20integration=20?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=E2=80=94=20path=5Fexists,=20ReadDir=20stream,=20no=20lockfile,?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20tar=20stubs?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- tools::path_exists(): sync Path::exists() always returns false on wasm
  (std::fs unsupported); route through the fs shim's in-memory table
- accounts: reuse the iOS no-lockfile cfg for wasm (fd-lock unavailable;
  Config::sync() no longer demands the lock task)
- tools/blob: ReadDirStream sites cfg'd (shim ReadDir implements Stream)
- imex: backup import/export bail on wasm until file-based IMEX (tar
  needs tokio/fs); key import/export unaffected
---
